DIAGNOSIS:
  -2.289989454992704e+226 = 0xEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE = cuMemsetD8 0xee sentinel fill.
  The kernel ran successfully (sync OK, 0 errors) but its body has no
  ld.global.f64 / st.global.f64 to materialize the vec-add. The source
  `c[to_i64(gid)] = a[to_i64(gid)] + b[to_i64(gid)]` should produce
  STMT_LOAD x2 + STMT_ADD + STMT_STORE in MIR, but the codegen-side
  STMT_LOAD/STORE emission for source-derived MIR is not wired (this
  fixture works only with the synthetic lower_test MIR shape).

